Ultra Low Power Asynchronous MAC Protocol using Wake-Up Radio for Energy Neutral WSN

Trong Nhan Le
University of Rennes 1, INRIA
trong-nhan.le@irisa.fr
Olivier Berder
University of Rennes 1, INRIA
oberder@irisa.fr

